"A young Knight, Deoran, is dispatched to take command of the South Guard...  "
"Note:  This campaign is designed as an introduction to Wesnoth.  The "
"'Civilian' difficulty level is aimed at first-time players."
msgstr ""
"Mladi vitez, Deoran, beše otposlat da preuzme zapovedanje Južnjačkom "
"gardom... Napomena: Ovaj pohod je projektovan kao uvod u Vesnot. Nivo težine "
"„civil“ namenjen je igračima koji igraju po prvi put."

